Endpoint Tickets:

- **General User Access:**
    - **GET**/tickets dan**GET**/tickets/{id}
- **Admin/Superuser Access:**
    - **POST, PUT**, dan**DELETE**/tickets/{id}

Endpoint Registrations:

- **General User Access:**
    - **POST** /registrations dan **GET** /registrations/{id}
- **Admin/Superuser Access:**
    - **GET, PUT**, dan **DELETE** /registrations/{id}

Endpoint Payments:

- **General User Access:  
    POST** /payments dan **GET** /payments/{id}
- **Admin/Superuser Access:  
    GET, PUT,** dan **DELETE** /payments/{id}
